<section class="page-section faq-page">
  <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
  <h1>Guide Market FAQ</h1>
  <details open>
    <summary>What is Guide Market?</summary>
    <p>Guide Market is a digital store for practical guides focused on better habits, money decisions, energy, and self-improvement.</p>
  </details>
  <details>
    <summary>Are the products digital?</summary>
    <p>Yes. The products are digital guides designed to be read and used on your phone, tablet, or computer.</p>
  </details>
  <details>
    <summary>Which products are available?</summary>
    <p>The store includes guides such as Stop Being Broke, Broke by Habit, and Stop Feeling Drained, depending on what is currently published in the shop.</p>
  </details>
  <details>
    <summary>How do I receive my purchase?</summary>
    <p>After checkout, access and delivery details are handled through Shopify. Check the email used at checkout for order information.</p>
  </details>
  <details>
    <summary>Can I use the guides immediately?</summary>
    <p>Yes. The guides are built to be simple to start, with clear sections and practical action steps.</p>
  </details>
  <details>
    <summary>Do you offer refunds?</summary>
    <p>Refunds for digital products depend on the order status, delivery status, and the issue reported. Contact Guide Market with your order details for help.</p>
  </details>
  <details>
    <summary>How can I contact Guide Market?</summary>
    <p>Email <strong>guidemarket.com@gmail.com</strong> or use the contact form.</p>
  </details>
</section>

